{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_03",
  "title": "ありのままの\n想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――歌詞制作が始まって、数日後……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days after the lyric production began……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.6800001144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あまりしっくりこうへんなぁ\n回りくどいって言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It doesn't quite feel right.\nIt's like going around in circles…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "endTime": 10.2193650882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……\nでも、ストレート過ぎるとチープになりそうだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…\nBut if it's too straightforward‚ it might feel cheap…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "endTime": 16.6131293615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "逆に、こういう表現はどうかな？\nうまく間を取れてると思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about this expression?\nI think it strikes a good balance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8,
      "endTime": 23.4402719498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに\n……あ、でも待って。前後の脈絡が少し変になるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true.\n…Oh‚ but wait. The context before and after might get a little awkward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333333333,
      "endTime": 30.4485034307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………う～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6333333333,
      "endTime": 32.6778457721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "このまま唸っとってもしゃあないし\n少し休憩でもしよか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no point just grumbling like this.\nShould we take a short break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1666666667,
      "endTime": 38.220385519699995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。……作詞って、想像以上に難しいわね\nもちろん、簡単とも思ってなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Writing lyrics is more difficult than I imagined.\nOf course‚ I didn't think it would be easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "endTime": 47.1228120168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "語彙力、メロディーとの兼ね合い、コンセプト……\nいろんなこと考えなあかんからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Vocabulary‚ balance with melody‚ concept…\nThere are many things to consider.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3333333333,
      "endTime": 55.205555566099996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "伝えたいこととか言葉にしたいことって\nホントは沢山あるんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many things I want to convey and express in words.\nBut I can't put everything into lyrics‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4,
      "endTime": 62.452040863099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "全部は詞に起こせないし、ただ、欠けてもダメだし……\nうわーん、難しいよぅ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and even if something is missing‚ it won't work…\nUwaaan‚ it's difficult!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6666666667,
      "endTime": 72.767936198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "（どうするのがいいんだろう）\n（私達だけじゃ、実力が伴ってない？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What should we do?)\n(Do we lack the skills to do this on our own?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9666666667,
      "endTime": 79.1955554644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "（……いや、そんな弱気じゃダメ）\n（まだ、出来ることはあるはず）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…No‚ being so pessimistic won't help)\n(There must still be something we can do)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4,
      "endTime": 84.3255555153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "いっそのこと、誰かに相談してみる？\n{user}さんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about asking someone else?\nLike {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "endTime": 89.5638321241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……\nさくらちゃん達サニピも、作詞経験あるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah…\nSakura-chan and the Sunny Peace girls have experience in writing lyrics‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7666666667,
      "endTime": 95.0798187892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね\nさすがに三人だけで考えるのも限界だし……よしっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's true.\nPerhaps relying on just the three of us won't be enough… Alright.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2666666667,
      "endTime": 101.31580502199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様……ってどうした？\nどこか出掛けるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… Oh‚ what's up?\nAre you going somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5,
      "endTime": 106.3181179047,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……{user}さん\n実は、ちょうど相談しに行こうと思ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… {user}-san.\nActually‚ we was just about to go and ask for help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5333333333,
      "endTime": 111.7762811979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "相談……作詞に関してか？\n結構苦戦していたようだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Help… about lyrics?\nYou seemed to be struggling quite a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666666667,
      "endTime": 117.89113356269999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あら、知っとったのに声も掛けず静観してたん？\n人が悪いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ so you knew and just silently watched?\nYou're quite mean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1,
      "endTime": 124.82215442660001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "頼る前に助け船を出されるのも、悔しいだろ？\n頃合いを見計らってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be frustrating to be thrown a lifeline before asking for help‚ right?\nI was waiting for the right timing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "endTime": 130.731156667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "それは……おっしゃる通りですが……\n手玉にとられているようで、どっちにしろ悔しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… true‚ but…\nIt feels like we are being manipulated‚ and either way‚ it's frustrating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9333333333,
      "endTime": 138.4689113935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん\nでもちょうど良かった。彼女が会いたいって言ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ I'm so sorry.\nBut it's a good timing. She wants to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6666666667,
      "endTime": 144.4942178408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "彼女……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7,
      "endTime": 145.9588662386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは\n作詞、苦戦してるって聞いて、心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello.\nI heard you were struggling with lyrics‚ and I was worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1666666667,
      "endTime": 152.03333333330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ミクちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2333333333,
      "endTime": 153.78551021410001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "実は俺も、ミクにこっそり相談してたんだ\nそしたら、ぜひ会って話がしたいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I secretly asked Miku as well.\nAnd she said she wanted to meet and talk with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154,
      "endTime": 160.5478685379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "良かったら、今の状況、話してくれない？\n何か、アドバイスが出来るかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's alright‚ could you tell me about the current situation?\nMaybe I can give some advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.7333333333,
      "endTime": 167.799942213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか。いろいろ考え過ぎちゃってるんだね\nそれで、がんじがらめになって、詞もぎこちなく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. You've been overthinking things‚ haven't you?\nThat's why you've been trapped and the lyrics feel awkward…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1333333333,
      "endTime": 179.82769574160002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。伝えたいことや贈りたい想いが、絞れなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I can't narrow down the things I want to convey and the feelings I want to give.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180,
      "endTime": 185.3817008018,
