    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね……私から、何か言えるとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.5666666667,
      "endTime": 191.13333333330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "難しく考えなくても、大丈夫だと思うな\n想いは素直に、ありのままに、綴ればいいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it's okay not to think too much.\nJust express your feelings honestly and as they are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3,
      "endTime": 200.26104316709998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "素直に、ありのままに……？\nでもそれじゃあ、キレイにまとまらないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly and as they are…?\nBut won't it be messy and not well put-together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.4666666667,
      "endTime": 208.4899094264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "最初はそうかもしれない……でもそういった形はね\n後からついてきて出来上がるものだって思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be true at first… but I believe that such forms\ncome together and take shape as you go along.",
        "id": ""
