      "text": "後からついてきて、出来上がる……\nそんな風に考えたこと、なかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Coming together and taking shape as you go along…\nI've never thought about it that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.7333333333,
      "endTime": 223.8909750303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
